flowchart LR
    U([User / 用户]) --> I[Task Intake / 任务入口]
    I --> C[Control Center / 总控中心]
    C --> P[Planning Center / 规划中心]
    P --> R[Review Center / 评审中心]
    R --> D[Dispatch Center / 调度中心]
    D --> S[Specialist Execution / 专业执行组]
    S --> A[Result Archive / 结果归档]
    A --> O([Delivery / 交付])

    R -. revision .-> P
    D -. monitor .-> S

    classDef main fill:#0f172a,stroke:#60a5fa,color:#e5eefc,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef io fill:#0b3b2e,stroke:#34d399,color:#eafff7,stroke-width:1.5px;
    class U,O io;
    class I,C,P,R,D,S,A main;
